# Curated, checked-in regression seeds live in this directory (as `*.js`).
#
# `cargo fuzz` / libFuzzer writes new corpus entries using hash-like filenames without extensions.
# If a developer accidentally points the fuzzer at this directory as its *output* corpus, we'd
# rather ignore those generated files than spam `git status` with hundreds of entries.
*
!*.js
!.gitignore
